{
  "texts": [
    "Chatbot technology has become ubiquitous, being used in several domains, such as customer service and personal virtual assistants.",
    "Modern computers possess immense computational capacity, enabling large language models (LLMs) to contain hundreds of billions of parameters.",
    "These parameters can be utilized to generate fresh textual content.",
    "The capacity to utilize a vast quantity of accessible (Internet) data for training the network allows language models to expand their capabilities continuously (4).",
    "Several AI chatbots, including ChatGPT and BingAI, are widely available and actively developed by AI research and development companies."
  ]
}